[42.061852, "o", "t?\u001b[0m\u001b[15;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[2m[\u001b[0m\u001b[92m✓\u001b[0m\u001b[2m] \u001b[0m\u001b[1;97mIteration 1 / 100\u001b[0m  \u001b[2m(34799 tok)\u001b[0m  \u001b[2m(14.5s)\u001b[0m\u001b[16;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[2m  Think: \u001b[0m\u001b[2mThe question has two parts: (1) user-defined agents in this project — use meta-agent$list; \u001b[0m\u001b[17;1H\u001b[2K         \u001b[2m(2) built-in specialists — use list-tools filtered to type \"agent\". These are independent, \u001b[0m\u001b[18;1H\u001b[2K         \u001b[2mso I'll fire both in one iteration.\u001b[0m\u001b[19;1H\u001b[2K  \u001b[36m→\u001b[0m \u001b[1;36mmeta-agent$list\u001b[0m({}): called \u001b[2m→\u001b[0m \u001b[92mdone\u001b[0m, 4ms, 12 chars\u001b[20;1H\u001b[2K  \u001b[36m→\u001b[0m \u001b[1;36mlist-tools\u001b[0m({\"type\" \"agent\"}): called \u001b[2m→\u001b[0m \u001b[92mdone\u001b[0m, 4ms, 17.4k chars\u001b[21;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[2m[\u001b[0m\u001b[1;96m+\u001b[0m\u001b[2m] \u001b[0m\u001b[1;97mIteration 2 / 100\u001b[0m  \u001b[2m(42397 tok)\u001b[0m  \u001b[2m(17.3s)\u001b[0m\u001b[22;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[2m  Think: \u001b[0m\u001b[2mBoth queries already ran in iteration 1: meta-agent$list returned `{:agents []}` (no \u001b[0m\u001b[23;1H\u001b[2K         \u001b[2muser-defined agents), and list-tools type \"agent\" returned the 22 built-in specialists. I \u001b[0m\u001b[24;1H\u001b[2K         \u001b[2mhave"]
