[168.576745, "o", "\u001b[1;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m   • \u001b[1;97mTools it reaches for:\u001b[0m \u001b[36mread-file\u001b[0m (chunked via \u001b[36m:lines\u001b[0m/\u001b[36m:offset\u001b[0m for large files), \u001b[36mgrep\u001b[0m (locate   \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\u001b[2;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m     headings/keywords when a file is too big to load whole).                                     \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\u001b[3;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m   • \u001b[1;97mSafety:\u001b[0m read-only — never modifies/executes files; summarizes secrets' nature without        \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\u001b[4;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m     reproducing values.                                                                          \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\u001b[5;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m                                                                                                  \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\u001b[6;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m \u001b[1;97mVerified with\u001b[0m                                                                                    \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\u001b[7;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m \u001b[2m\u001b[32m│ \u001b[0m\u001b[3m\"Summarize the file at …/.brainyard/BRAINYARD.md in a single sentence.\"\u001b[0m                        \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m"]
[168.576759, "o", "\u001b[8;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m                                                                                                  \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\u001b[9;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m → \u001b[3m\"The file is the brainyard project's preferences and orientation guide, documenting the\u001b[0m        \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\u001b[10;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m \u001b[3mPolylith workspace's scope overrides, repository structure, build/runtime conventions,\u001b[0m           \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\u001b[11;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m \u001b[3mregistered agent types, and an index of key documentation for AI assistants working in the\u001b[0m       \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\u001b[12;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m \u001b[3mrepo.\"\u001b[0m                                                                                           \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\u001b[13;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m                                                                                                  \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\u001b[14;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m A correct, single-sentence summary — the agent works as intended.                                \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\u001b[15;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m                                    "]
[168.5768, "o", "                                                              \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\u001b[16;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m \u001b[1;97mUse it:\u001b[0m \u001b[36muser$agent$line-summarizer\u001b[0m with \u001b[36m{:question \"Summarize the file at <path> in a single\u001b[0m     \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\u001b[17;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m \u001b[36msentence.\"}\u001b[0m                                                                                      \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\u001b[18;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[92m└──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\u001b[0m\u001b[19;1H\u001b[2K  \u001b[1;92m✓ Goal achieved\u001b[0m\u001b[20;1H\u001b[2K  \u001b[2m↳ Try next: Try line-summarizer on docs/architecture.md\u001b[0m\u001b[21;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[22;1H\u001b[2K                                                                 \u001b[2m8 calls │ 240,496 tokens │ $1.4003\u001b[0m\u001b[23;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[24;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[1m\u001b[96m\u001b[100m❯ Read back the line-summarizer age"]
