[181.207774, "o", "\u001b[1;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m → \u001b[3m\"The file is the brainyard project's preferences and orientation guide, documenting the\u001b[0m        \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\u001b[2;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m \u001b[3mPolylith workspace's scope overrides, repository structure, build/runtime conventions,\u001b[0m           \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\u001b[3;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m \u001b[3mregistered agent types, and an index of key documentation for AI assistants working in the\u001b[0m       \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\u001b[4;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m \u001b[3mrepo.\"\u001b[0m                                                                                           \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\u001b[5;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m                                                                                                  \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\u001b[6;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m A correct, single-sentence summary — the agent works as intended.                                \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\u001b[7;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m                                                                                                  \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\u001b[8;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m \u001b[1;97mUse it:\u001b[0m \u001b[36muser$agent$line-s"]
