[241.855949, "o", "\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\u001b[7;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m \u001b[1;97mScope\u001b[0m            \u001b[2m │ \u001b[0m\u001b[36m:project\u001b[0m — \u001b[36m.brainyard/agents/user$agent/line-summarizer/\u001b[0m                     \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\u001b[8;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m \u001b[1;97mVersion\u001b[0m          \u001b[2m │ \u001b[0m1                                                                            \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\u001b[9;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m \u001b[1;97mCreated / Updated\u001b[0m\u001b[2m │ \u001b[0m2026-06-11T14:11:10Z                                                         \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\u001b[10;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m                                                                                                  \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\u001b[11;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m   • \u001b[1;97mRole line:\u001b[0m \u001b[3m\"Given a file path, you read that file and return a SINGLE-SENTENCE summary of\u001b[0m    \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\u001b[12;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m     \u001b[3mits contents. Nothing more.\"\u001b[0m                                                                 \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\u001b[13;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m   • \u001b[1;97mDecision flow:\u001b[0m extract path (ask if missing) → \u001b[36mread-file\u001b"]
[241.855962, "o", "[0m (chunk large files via              \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\u001b[14;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m     \u001b[36m:lines\u001b[0m/\u001b[36m:offset\u001b[0m, or \u001b[36mgrep\u001b[0m headings) → distill to one dense sentence → return it with no        \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\u001b[15;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m     headers/bullets.                                                                             \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\u001b[16;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m   • \u001b[1;97mTools it reaches for:\u001b[0m \u001b[36mread-file\u001b[0m (primary), \u001b[36mgrep\u001b[0m (locate headings in large files).            \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\u001b[17;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m   • \u001b[1;97mSafety:\u001b[0m read-only — never modifies/moves/deletes, never executes file contents, never        \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\u001b[18;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m     reproduces secret values.                                                                    \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\u001b[19;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m                                                                                                  \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\u001b[20;1H\u001b[2K\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m \u001b[2m───────────────────────"]
