[241.877682, "o", "\r\n\u001b[2m┌────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[2m│\u001b[0m \u001b[1m\u001b[96mBrainyard TUI\u001b[0m\u001b[2m — \u001b[0m\u001b[1m\u001b[36mmeta-agent\u001b[0m\u001b[2m · \u001b[0m\u001b[95mclaude-code/opus\u001b[0m\u001b[2m · \u001b[0m\u001b[2msession tutorial-24-agents\u001b[0m \u001b[2m│\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[2m│\u001b[0m \u001b[2mType /help for commands. AI output may be inaccurate.\u001b[0m                      \u001b[2m│\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[2m└────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n\u001b[1m\u001b[96m\u001b[100m❯ What user-defined agents are registered in this project, and which built-in specialists already\r\n  exist?\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[2m[\u001b[0m\u001b[92m✓\u001b[0m\u001b[2m] \u001b[0m\u001b[1;97mIteration 1 / 100\u001b[0m  \u001b[2m(34799 tok)\u001b[0m  \u001b[2m(14.5s)\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[2m  Think: \u001b[0m\u001b[2mThe"]
[241.877691, "o", " question has two parts: (1) user-defined agents in this project — use meta-agent$list; \u001b[0m\r\n         \u001b[2m(2) built-in specialists — use list-tools filtered to type \"agent\". These are independent, \u001b[0m\r\n         \u001b[2mso I'll fire both in one iteration.\u001b[0m\r\n  \u001b[36m→\u001b[0m \u001b[1;36mmeta-agent$list\u001b[0m({}): called \u001b[2m→\u001b[0m \u001b[92mdone\u001b[0m, 4ms, 12 chars\r\n  \u001b[36m→\u001b[0m \u001b[1;36mlist-tools\u001b[0m({\"type\" \"agent\"}): called \u001b[2m→\u001b[0m \u001b[92mdone\u001b[0m, 4ms, 17.4k chars\r\n\u001b[2m[\u001b[0m\u001b[92m✓\u001b[0m\u001b[2m] \u001b[0m\u001b[1;97mIteration 2 / 100\u001b[0m  \u001b[2m(58168 tok)\u001b[0m  \u001b[2m(32.8s)\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[2m  Think: \u001b[0m\u001b[2mThe evidence shows meta-agent$list returned {:agents []}, confirming no user-defined \u001b[0m\r\n         \u001b[2magents — the answer correctly states \"None\" and cites the user$agent/ path (which appears \u001b[0m\r\n         \u001b[2min the tool-context). The list-tools call returned 22 built-in agents: exec, skill, tool, \u001b[0m\r\n         \u001b[2mworkflow, memory, main, mcp, meta, explore, rlm, debug, init, eval, coact, acp, config, \u001b[0m\r\n         \u001b[2mresearc"]
[241.877737, "o", "h, update, hook, react, plan, todo. Counting them gives exactly 22, matching the \u001b[0m\r\n         \u001b[2manswer's claim. Each role description in the table accurately summarizes the corresponding \u001b[0m\r\n         \u001b[2magent's description from the evidence. No fabricated values or contradictions.\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[2m\r\n  │ Evaluating answer quality (round 0)...\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[2m  │ Checking against sandbox evidence (17232 chars) via LLM...\u001b[0m\r\n  \u001b[1;92m✓ PASS — answer verified\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n\u001b[92m┌────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m \u001b[1;97mUser-Defined Agents (this project)\u001b[0m                                                             \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m                                                                                                \u001b[92m│\u001b"]
[241.877746, "o", "[0m\r\n\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m \u001b[1;97mNone.\u001b[0m \u001b[36mmeta-agent$list\u001b[0m returns an empty set — no persistent agents have been authored under     \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m \u001b[36m<project>/.brainyard/agents/user$agent/\u001b[0m yet. If you'd like one, I can author it (instruction + \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m tool-context, validated and verified).                                                         \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m                                                                                                \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m \u001b[1;97mBuilt-In Specialists (22 registered)\u001b[0m                                                           \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m                                                                                                \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m \u001b[1;97mAgent\u001b[0m         \u001b[2m │ \u001b[0m\u001b[1;97mRole\u001b[0m                                                                          \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m \u001b[2m───────────────┼────────"]
[241.877772, "o", "────────────────────────────────────────────────────\u001b[0m                   \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m \u001b[36mmain-agent\u001b[0m    \u001b[2m │ \u001b[0mFront-door router → picks the right specialist per question                   \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m \u001b[36mcoact-agent\u001b[0m   \u001b[2m │ \u001b[0mReasoning + Code + Action loop (3 channels)                                   \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m \u001b[36mreact-agent\u001b[0m   \u001b[2m │ \u001b[0mReAct — one LLM call per iteration                                            \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m \u001b[36mresearch-agent\u001b[0m\u001b[2m │ \u001b[0mMulti-specialist research loop with durable dossier                           \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m \u001b[36mworkflow-agent\u001b[0m\u001b[2m │ \u001b[0mDomain multi-stage workflow loop (templated stages)                           \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m \u001b[36mexplore-agent\u001b[0m \u001b[2m │ \u001b[0mRead-mostly exploration (filesystem / web / MCP / skills)                  "]
[241.877812, "o", "   \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m \u001b[36mplan-agent\u001b[0m    \u001b[2m │ \u001b[0mAuthor plan blueprints with pre/post-flight grading                           \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m \u001b[36mtodo-agent\u001b[0m    \u001b[2m │ \u001b[0mAuthor/advance executable todos with gating                                   \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m \u001b[36mexec-agent\u001b[0m    \u001b[2m │ \u001b[0mDrive a todo list to completion, tag-based routing                            \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m \u001b[36meval-agent\u001b[0m    \u001b[2m │ \u001b[0mScore executed todos against plan acceptance criteria                         \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m \u001b[36mupdate-agent\u001b[0m  \u001b[2m │ \u001b[0mSafe single-file edits (probe→apply→verify→rollback)                          \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m \u001b[36mdebug-agent\u001b[0m   \u001b[2m │ \u001b[0mLive-runtime nREPL debug loop against the running JVM                         \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m \u001b[36mmemory-agent\u001b[0m  \u001b[2m │ \u001b[0mSteward of the layered memory stack                                           \u001b[92m│\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[92m│\u001b[0m \u001b"]
